  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK375">
<l>nallavai yellāan tīyavān tīyavu</l>
<l>nallavāñ celvañ ceyaṟku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the acquisition of property, every thing favourable becomes unfavourable, and (on the other hand) everything unfavourable becomes favourable, (through the power of fate).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
